  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Enjoy a sumptuous breakfast buffet including fresh roasted coffee, a selection of teas, fresh fruits and juices, bread, milk and cheeses straight from local farms, homemade jams and hot items too.</p>
<p>The five-course half board evening meal offers the finest selection of freshly sourced ingredients. Enjoy classic European cuisine and regional dishes with a modern twist.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
